    'template_game_class_warrior_story' => '<p>For as long as war has raged, heroes from every race have aimed to master the art of battle. Warriors combine strength, leadership, and a vast knowledge of arms and armor to wreak havoc in glorious combat. Some protect from the front lines with shields, locking down enemies while allies support the warrior from behind with spell and bow. Others forgo the shield and unleash their rage at the closest threat with a variety of deadly weapons.</p>',
    'template_game_class_warrior_story_long' => '<p>The warrior’s battle cries embolden friends and leave foes cowering in fear. With legendary precision, warriors target the smallest gaps in armor and slice at hamstrings in a blur of steel.</p><p>Every dragon slain, corrupted tyrant toppled, and demon banished from Azeroth has trembled in the face of these lords of war.</p>',
    'template_game_class_warrior_information' => 'Warriors equip themselves carefully for combat and engage their enemies head-on, letting attacks glance off their heavy armor. They use diverse combat tactics and a wide variety of weapon types to protect their more vulnerable allies. Warriors must carefully master their rage – the power behind their strongest attacks – in order to maximize their effectiveness in combat.',
    'template_game_class_warrior_type' => 'Tank, Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_warrior_bars' => 'Health, Rage',
    'template_game_class_warrior_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather, Mail, Plate, Shields',
    'template_game_class_warrior_weapons' => 'Bows, Crossbows, Daggers, Fist Weapons Guns, One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Maces, One-Handed Swords, Polearms,	Staves, Two-Handed Axes, Two-Handed Maces, Two-Handed Swords',
    'template_game_class_warrior_talents' => 'Warrior talents can improve their already considerable defenses with a shield, increase their deadliness with two-handed weapons, or bolster their savagery while dual-wielding.',
    'template_game_class_warrior_talent1' => 'Arms',
    'template_game_class_warrior_talent2' => 'Fury',
    'template_game_class_warrior_talent3' => 'Protection',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_title1' => 'Defense',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_desc1' => 'Mighty warriors depend on their heavy armor, shields, and battle prowess to defend themselves and ensure enemies don’t focus on their softer-skinned allies.',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_title2' => 'Melee damage',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_desc2' => 'Weapon mastery is a staple of warrior training, and they are capable of delivering high damage with enormous two-handed weapons or by wielding two weapons.',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_title3' => 'Rage',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_desc3' => 'As warriors deal or take damage, their rage grows, allowing them to deliver truly crushing attacks in the heat of battle.',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_title4' => 'Stances',
    'template_game_class_warrior_feature_desc4' => 'By changing their stance during battle, warriors can adjust their focus in combat, dealing greater damage, defending more carefully against enemy attacks, or striking a balance between the two.',
    
    'template_game_class_paladin_story' => '<p>This is the call of the paladin: to protect the weak, to bring justice to the unjust, and to vanquish evil from the darkest corners of the world. These holy warriors are equipped with plate armor so they can confront the toughest of foes, and the blessing of the Light allows them to heal wounds and, in some cases, even restore life to the dead.</p>',
    'template_game_class_paladin_story_long' => '<p>Ready to serve, paladins can defend their allies with sword and shield, or they can wield massive two-handed weapons against their enemies. The Light grants paladins additional power against the undead and demons, ensuring that these profane beings corrupt the world no longer.</p><p>Paladins are not only zealots, but also guardians of the righteous, and they bestow blessings on those the Light would shine upon. The Light radiates from paladins, and worthy allies who stand near them are emboldened by its power. </p>',
    'template_game_class_paladin_information' => 'Paladins stand directly in front of their enemies, relying on heavy armor and healing in order to survive incoming attacks. Whether with massive shields or crushing two-handed weapons, Paladins are able to keep claws and swords from their weaker fellows – or they use healing magic to ensure that they remain on their feet.',
    'template_game_class_paladin_type' => 'Tank, Healer, Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_paladin_bars' => 'Health, Mana',
    'template_game_class_paladin_armor' => 'Cloth, Mail,	Leather, Cloth, Plate, Shields',
    'template_game_class_paladin_weapons' => 'One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Maces, One-Handed Swords, Polearms, Two-Handed Axes, Two-Handed Maces, Two-Handed Swords, Relic',
    'template_game_class_paladin_talents' => 'Paladin talents increase their ability to heal the wounded, strengthen their capacity to protect their companions, and allow them to deal out vicious damage in the name of justice.',
    'template_game_class_paladin_talent1' => 'Holy',
    'template_game_class_paladin_talent2' => 'Protection',
    'template_game_class_paladin_talent3' => 'Retribution',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_title1' => 'Defense',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_desc1' => 'Stalwart paladins are trained to use the heaviest armor and shields, and can utilize their skill to ensure that enemies focus on them, defending weaker members of their group.',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_title2' => 'Melee damage',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_desc2' => 'Paladins charge their weapons with holy might, allowing them to deal additional damage with their strikes.',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_title3' => 'Auras, Blessings, and Seals',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_desc3' => 'As champions of order, paladins are extremely potent in a group – their auras, blessings and seals can improve damage and survivability for both themselves and their party.',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_title4' => 'Healing',
    'template_game_class_paladin_feature_desc4' => 'Paladins’ potent healing abilities can ensure that they and their allies remain in fighting shape.',
    
    'template_game_class_hunter_story' => '<p>From an early age the call of the wild draws some adventurers from the comfort of their homes into the unforgiving primal world outside. Those who endure become hunters. Masters of their environment, they are able to slip like ghosts through the trees and lay traps in the paths of their enemies.</p>',
    'template_game_class_hunter_story_long' => '<p>These expert marksmen drop foes dead in their tracks with flawless shots from a bow or rifle. With the ability to wield two weapons simultaneously, hunters can unleash a flurry of blows against anyone unfortunate enough to stumble into close combat with them. </p><p>The art of survival is central to the isolated life of a hunter. Hunters track beasts with ease and enhance their own abilities by attuning themselves to the feral aspects of various creatures. Hunters are known for the lifelong bonds they form with animals of the wild, training great hawks, cats, bears, and many other beasts to fight alongside them.</p>',
    'template_game_class_hunter_information' => 'Hunters battle their foes at a distance, commanding their pets to attack while they nock their arrows and fire their guns. Though their missile weapons are extremely effective, hunters are at a disadvantage when their foes close in, and often attempt to evade or restrain enemies so that they can continue fighting from a safe distance.',
    'template_game_class_hunter_type' => 'Ranged Physical Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_hunter_bars' => 'Health, Focus',
    'template_game_class_hunter_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather, Mail',
    'template_game_class_hunter_weapons' => 'Bows, Crossbows, Fist Weapons, Guns, One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Swords, Polearms, Staves, Two-Handed Axes, Two-Handed Swords',
    'template_game_class_hunter_talents' => 'Hunter talents primarily strengthen their pets; improve the damage, effectiveness, and duration of their traps; and increase the speed and power of their ranged attacks.',
    'template_game_class_hunter_talent1' => 'Beast Mastery',
    'template_game_class_hunter_talent2' => 'Marksmanship',
    'template_game_class_hunter_talent3' => 'Survival',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_title1' => 'Pets',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_desc1' => 'Hunters tame the beasts of the wild, and those beasts serve in return by assaulting their enemies and shielding them from harm.',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_title2' => 'Ranged damage',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_desc2' => 'Whether wielding bows, guns, or crossbows, hunters are deadly with ranged weapons. They are capable of dishing out consistently high damage.',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_title3' => 'Traps',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_desc3' => 'Hunters are consummate survivalists, able to set traps to burn, freeze, and disable potential prey.',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_title4' => 'Soloing',
    'template_game_class_hunter_feature_desc4' => 'Thanks to their pets and damage output, hunters are effective at completing quests and leveling quickly, even when they’re alone.',
    
    'template_game_class_rogue_story' => '<p>For rogues, the only code is the contract, and their honor is purchased in gold. Free from the constraints of a conscience, these mercenaries rely on brutal and efficient tactics. Lethal assassins and masters of stealth, they will approach their marks from behind, piercing a vital organ and vanishing into the shadows before the victim hits the ground.</p>',
    'template_game_class_rogue_story_long' => '<p>Rogues can dip their weapons in paralyzing toxins that render foes unable to defend themselves. These silent stalkers wear leather armor so they can move unencumbered, ensuring that they land the first strike.</p><p>With the rogue’s poisons and speed, the first strike is often the last step before the killing blow.</p>',
    'template_game_class_rogue_information' => 'Rogues often initiate combat with a surprise attack from the shadows, leading with vicious melee strikes. When in protracted battles, they utilize a successive combination of carefully chosen attacks to soften the enemy up for a killing blow. Rogues must take special care when selecting targets so that their combo attacks are not wasted, and they must be conscious of when to hide or flee if a battle turns against them.',
    'template_game_class_rogue_type' => 'Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_rogue_bars' => 'Health, Energy',
    'template_game_class_rogue_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather',
    'template_game_class_rogue_weapons' => 'Bows, Crossbows, Daggers, Fist Weapons, One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Maces, One-Handed Swords',
    'template_game_class_rogue_talents' => 'Rogue talents can strengthen their ability to hide in shadows, kill foes with quick, deadly strikes, and survive in extended slugfests.',
    'template_game_class_rogue_talent1' => 'Assassination',
    'template_game_class_rogue_talent2' => 'Combat',
    'template_game_class_rogue_talent3' => 'Subtlety',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_title1' => 'Stealth',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_desc1' => 'Rogues sneak about the battlefield, hiding from enemies and delivering surprise attacks to the unwary when opportunity arises.',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_title2' => 'Melee damage',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_desc2' => 'By coating their dual-wielded blades with deadly poisons, rogues can deliver catastrophic damage to their targets.',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_title3' => 'Evasion',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_desc3' => 'When endangered, rogues have many tools at their disposal to avoid their enemies’ gaze and, if necessary, their attacks.',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_title4' => 'Combos',
    'template_game_class_rogue_feature_desc4' => 'By planning and combining successive melee attacks, rogues can build up combo points that allow them to deliver devastating finishing blows in combat.',
    
    'template_game_class_priest_story' => '<p>Priests are devoted to the spiritual, and express their unwavering faith by serving the people. For millennia they have left behind the confines of their temples and the comfort of their shrines so they can support their allies in war-torn lands. In the midst of terrible conflict, no hero questions the value of the priestly orders.</p>',
    'template_game_class_priest_story_long' => '<p>These masters of the healing arts keep their companions fighting far beyond their normal capacities with an array of restorative powers and blessings. The divine forces at the priest’s command can also be turned against foes, smiting them with holy fury.</p><p>As light cannot exist without darkness, and darkness without light, some priests tap into shadow to better understand their own abilities, as well as the abilities of those who threaten them.</p>',
    'template_game_class_priest_information' => 'Priests use powerful healing magic to fortify themselves and their allies. They also wield powerful offensive spells from a distance, but can be overwhelmed by enemies due to their physical frailty and minimal armor. Experienced priests carefully balance the use of their offensive powers when tasked with keeping their party alive.',
    'template_game_class_priest_type' => 'Healer, Ranged Magic Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_priest_bars' => 'Health, Mana',
    'template_game_class_priest_armor' => 'Cloth',
    'template_game_class_priest_weapons' => 'Daggers, One-Handed Maces, Staves, Wands',
    'template_game_class_priest_talents' => 'Priest talents can strengthen their ability to heal the wounded, endanger their foes with the power of Shadow, or empower themselves and others with protective prayers.',
    'template_game_class_priest_talent1' => 'Discipline',
    'template_game_class_priest_talent2' => 'Holy',
    'template_game_class_priest_talent3' => 'Shadow',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_title1' => 'Healing',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_desc1' => 'Priests utilize their holy powers to restore their health and that of their comrades.',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_title2' => 'Ranged damage',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_desc2' => 'Priestly Shadow magic can deliver great amounts of immediate damage, or wracking pains that punish foes over longer periods of time.',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_title3' => 'Power words',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_desc3' => 'By calling on mystic shielding and holy empowerment, priests can prevent incoming damage and improve their defenses and those of their allies.',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_title4' => 'Mind Control',
    'template_game_class_priest_feature_desc4' => 'Priests’ connection with the minds and spirits of living beings allows them to control and manipulate others.',
    
    'template_game_class_death-knight_story' => '<p>When the Lich King’s control of his death knights was broken, his former champions sought revenge for the horrors committed under his command. After their vengeance was won, the death knights found themselves without a cause and without a home. One by one they trickled into the land of the living in search of a new purpose.</p>',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_story_long' => '<p>Frost sharpens their strikes; blood fortifies their bodies; and undeath allows them to erupt in unholy rage in the heat of battle. A thousand atrocities are etched in the eyes of every death knight, and foes who gaze into them too long will feel the warmth pulled from their bodies, replaced with cold steel.</p>',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_information' => 'Death Knights engage their foes up-close, supplementing swings of their weapons with dark magic that renders enemies vulnerable or damages them with unholy power. They drag foes into one-on-one conflicts, compelling them to focus their attacks away from weaker companions. To prevent their enemies from fleeing their grasp, death knights must remain mindful of the power they call forth from runes, and pace their attacks appropriately.',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_type' => 'Tank, Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_bars' => 'Health, Runic',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather, Mail, Plate',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_weapons' => 'One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Maces, One-Handed Swords, Polearms, Relic, Two-Handed Axes, Two-Handed Maces, Two-Handed Swords',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_talents' => 'Death knight talents can bolster their defensive abilities by focusing on their ability to heal themselves with blood runes , increase their damage and spell attacks with frost runes, or summon forth minions and diseases with unholy runes.',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_talent1' => 'Blood',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_talent2' => 'Frost',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_talent3' => 'Unholy',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_title1' => 'Defense',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_desc1' => 'To protect themselves and their fellows from death in battle, death knights gird themselves in heavy armor and parry attacks with their blades.',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_title2' => 'Melee damage',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_desc2' => 'Death knight runeblades are empowered with dark magic; they can expend the power of their runes for vicious attacks.',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_title3' => 'Utility',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_desc3' => 'As former champions of the Lich King, death knights can command the dead as minions, freeze their foes with ice, and inflict weakening diseases.',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_title4' => 'Runeforging',
    'template_game_class_death-knight_feature_desc4' => 'Death knights have a personal connection with their blades, and can forge runes into them in order to increase their power.',
    
    'template_game_class_shaman_story' => '<p>Shaman are spiritual guides and practitioners, not of the divine, but of the very elements. Unlike some other mystics, shaman commune with forces that are not strictly benevolent. The elements are chaotic, and left to their own devices, they rage against one another in unending primal fury. It is the call of the shaman to bring balance to this chaos. Acting as moderators among earth, fire, water, and air, shaman summon totems that focus the elements to support the shaman’s allies or punish those who threaten them.</p>',
    'template_game_class_shaman_story_long' => '<p>These masters of the elements can also call upon elemental forces directly, unleashing torrents of lava and bolts of lightning against foes. The elements can create, destroy, support, and hinder.</p><p>The experienced shaman balances the vast spectrum of these primordial forces into an array of diverse abilities, making shaman versatile heroes and valued members of any group.</p>',
    'template_game_class_shaman_information' => 'During combat, shaman place damaging and controlling totems on the ground to maximize their effectiveness while hindering their enemies. Shaman are versatile enough to battle foes up close or at range, but wise shaman choose their avenue of attack based on their enemies’ strengths and weaknesses.',
    'template_game_class_shaman_type' => 'Healer, Ranged Magic Damage Dealer, Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_shaman_bars' => 'Health, Mana',
    'template_game_class_shaman_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather, Mail, Shields',
    'template_game_class_shaman_weapons' => 'Daggers, Fist Weapons, One-Handed Axes, One-Handed Maces, Relic, Staves, Two-Handed Axes, Two-Handed Maces',
    'template_game_class_shaman_talents' => 'Shaman talents can strengthen their ability to heal the wounded, empower their melee attacks with natural force, or call upon blistering elemental spells.',
    'template_game_class_shaman_talent1' => 'Elemental',
    'template_game_class_shaman_talent2' => 'Enhancement',
    'template_game_class_shaman_talent3' => 'Restoration',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_title1' => 'Healing',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_desc1' => 'By calling on their spiritual power, shaman can restore health to injured allies.',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_title2' => 'Melee damage',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_desc2' => 'Shaman enhance their weapons with elemental effects, empowering their blows with the power of fire, wind, or ice.',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_title3' => 'Ranged damage',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_desc3' => 'Shaman can choose to deploy a wide array of different totems, each providing allies with a unique effect, including improved restoration, greater damage, faster attacks, and more.',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_title4' => 'Totems',
    'template_game_class_shaman_feature_desc4' => 'Shaman can choose to deploy a wide array of different totems, each providing allies with a unique effect, including improved restoration, greater damage, faster attacks, and more.',
    
    'template_game_class_mage_story' => '<p>Students gifted with a keen intellect and unwavering discipline may walk the path of the mage. The arcane magic available to magi is both great and dangerous, and thus is revealed only to the most devoted practitioners. To avoid interference with their spellcasting, magi wear only cloth armor, but arcane shields and enchantments give them additional protection. To keep enemies at bay, magi can summon bursts of fire to incinerate distant targets and cause entire areas to erupt, setting groups of foes ablaze.</p>',
    'template_game_class_mage_story_long' => '<p>Masters of ice can command blizzards that tear into flesh and limit movement. Should enemies manage to survive this assault, the mage can shrink them into harmless sheep in the blink of an eye.</p><p>Powerful magi can even generate enhancements and portals, assisting allies by sharpening their minds and transporting them instantly across the world.</p>',
    'template_game_class_mage_information' => 'Mages demolish their foes with arcane incantations. Although they wield powerful offensive spells, mages are fragile and lightly armored, making them particularly vulnerable to close-range attacks. Wise mages make careful use of their spells to keep their foes at a distance or hold them in place.',
    'template_game_class_mage_type' => 'Ranged Magic Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_mage_bars' => 'Health, Mana',
    'template_game_class_mage_armor' => 'Cloth',
    'template_game_class_mage_weapons' => 'Wands, Daggers, One-Handed Swords, Staves',
    'template_game_class_mage_talents' => 'Mage talents focus on enhancing individual schools of magic – quick, aggressive Fire spells; efficient, controlling Frost spells and punishing Arcane spells.',
    'template_game_class_mage_talent1' => 'Arcane',
    'template_game_class_mage_talent2' => 'Fire',
    'template_game_class_mage_talent3' => 'Frost',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_title1' => 'Ranged damage',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_desc1' => 'Mages can expend mana in order to deal high amounts of damage with amazing speed, though they must be wary of exhausting themselves.',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_title2' => 'Area of effect spells',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_desc2' => 'By calling upon sheets of ice, columns of flame, and waves of arcane power, mages can effectively attack multiple foes at the same time.',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_title3' => 'Control',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_desc3' => 'A mage has many options for controlling the battlefield, from freezing enemies in place to transforming them into helpless critters.',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_title4' => 'Teleportation',
    'template_game_class_mage_feature_desc4' => 'Mages possess the ability to transport themselves and their allies between cities and can summon replenishing food and water.',
    
    'template_game_class_warlock_story' => '<p>In the face of demonic power, most heroes see death. Warlocks see only opportunity. Dominance is their aim, and they have found a path to it in the dark arts. These voracious spellcasters summon demonic minions to fight beside them. At first, they command only the service of imps, but as a warlock’s knowledge grows, seductive succubi, loyal voidwalkers, and horrific felhunters join the dark sorcerer’s ranks to wreak havoc on anyone who stands in their master’s way.</p>',
    'template_game_class_warlock_story_long' => '<p>Warlocks can ignite distant enemies in searing flame, send them fleeing in terror and pain, or afflict them with corrupting diseases and curses that steal the victim’s vitality. </p><p>These practitioners of the profane are feared across Azeroth, and many who have felt their wrath now prefer to fight alongside a warlock than against one.</p>',
    'template_game_class_warlock_information' => 'Warlocks burn and destroy weakened foes with a combination of crippling illnesses and dark magic. While their demon pets protect and enhance them, warlocks strike at their enemies from a distance. As physically weak spellcasters bereft of heavy armor, cunning warlocks allow their minions to take the brunt of enemy attacks in order to save their own skin.',
    'template_game_class_warlock_type' => 'Ranged Magic Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_warlock_bars' => 'Health, Mana',
    'template_game_class_warlock_armor' => 'Cloth',
    'template_game_class_warlock_weapons' => 'Daggers, One-Handed Swords, Staves, Wands',
    'template_game_class_warlock_talents' => 'Warlock talents can improve the damage of their searing magics, increase the potency of their curses and persistent damaging spells, and empower their demonic servants.',
    'template_game_class_warlock_talent1' => 'Affliction',
    'template_game_class_warlock_talent2' => 'Demonology',
    'template_game_class_warlock_talent3' => 'Destruction',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_title1' => 'Pets',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_desc1' => 'Warlocks bind demons to their will; these infernal denizens defend their masters with their lives or rain death upon their enemies.',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_title2' => 'Curses and Drains',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_desc2' => 'Warlocks are able to curse their foes: slowing them, crippling their combat effectiveness, and weakening their resistance. They can also drain enemies’ health or mana to rejuvenate themselves.',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_title3' => 'Ranged Damage',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_desc3' => 'Warlocks deliver fire and shadow damage with their spells, and they’re able to hurt others both instantly and with ongoing afflictions.',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_title4' => 'Soul Shards',
    'template_game_class_warlock_feature_desc4' => 'Warlocks can drain enemy souls and use them to empower their own spells, making them swifter or more deadly.',
    
    'template_game_class_druid_story' => '<p>Druids harness the vast powers of nature to preserve balance and protect life. With experience, druids can unleash nature’s raw energy against their enemies, raining celestial fury on them from a great distance, binding them with enchanted vines, or ensnaring them in unrelenting cyclones.</p>',
    'template_game_class_druid_story_long' => '<p>Druids can also direct this power to heal wounds and restore life to fallen allies. They are deeply in tune with the animal spirits of Azeroth.</p><p>As master shapeshifters, druids can take on the forms of a variety of beasts, morphing into a bear, cat, storm crow, or sea lion with ease. This flexibility allows them to fill different roles during their adventures, tearing enemies to shreds one minute and surveying the battlefield from the sky the next. These keepers of the natural order are among the most versatile heroes in Azeroth, and they must be prepared to adjust to new challenges on a moment’s notice.</p>',
    'template_game_class_druid_information' => 'Druids are versatile combatants, in that they can fulfill nearly every role – healing, tanking, and damage dealing. It’s critical that druids tailor the form they choose to the situation, as each form bears a specific purpose.',
    'template_game_class_druid_type' => 'Tank, Healer, Ranged Magic Damage Dealer, Melee Damage Dealer',
    'template_game_class_druid_bars' => 'Health, Mana, Rage, Energy',
    'template_game_class_druid_armor' => 'Cloth, Leather',
    'template_game_class_druid_weapons' => 'Daggers, Fist Weapons, One-Handed Maces, Polearms, Relic, Staves, Two-Handed Maces',
    'template_game_class_druid_talents' => 'Druid talents focus on improving the powers of their natural and animal forms, enhancing their ability to summon forth natural phenomena, or increase the potency of their life-giving healing magic.',
    'template_game_class_druid_talent1' => 'Balance',
    'template_game_class_druid_talent2' => 'Feral',
    'template_game_class_druid_talent3' => 'Restoration',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_title1' => 'Versatility',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_desc1' => 'Druids’ changing forms let them assume different roles and focus on either tanking, healing, or damage. They can also shapeshift to travel faster on land, sea, and air.',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_title2' => 'Healing',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_desc2' => 'By calling upon the powers of nature, druids are able to swiftly restore health to their injured allies.',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_title3' => 'Defense',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_desc3' => 'When shapeshifted into their bear form, druids possess a thick skin and imposing presence that makes them ideal front-line protectors of weaker party members.',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_title4' => 'Melee and ranged damage',
    'template_game_class_druid_feature_desc4' => 'Druids can take on the form of a savage cat in order to claw and bite their enemies up close, or that of a wild moonkin to blast enemies from afar.',
    
    'template_game_class_artwork' => 'Artwork',
    'template_game_class_screenshots' => 'Screenshots',
    'template_game_class_more' => 'MORE INFORMATION',
    'template_game_class_more_desc' => 'Learn more about the Warrior on the following fansites.',
    'template_game_class_viewall' => 'View all',
    
    'template_menu_game_factions' => 'Factions',
    'template_menu_game_factions_intro' => 'Azeroth is a fractious and war-stricken world, and standing alone can be deadly. To survive and prosper, members of all races gather together along cultural and ideological lines. Each of these factions holds to a unique philosophy, and they often disagree with one another – violently. Yet, despite the danger, allegiance to a faction never goes unnoticed; those heroes who are willing to risk taking sides can expect handsome rewards.',
    'template_menu_game_factions_' => '',
    'template_menu_game_factions_' => '',
